import uniqid from 'uniqid' import { honors } from '../../portfolio' import './Honors.css' const Honors = () => { if (!honors.length) return null return (

Honors & Awards

{honors.map((honor) => (
{honor.year}

{honor.title}

{honor.organization}

{honor.description}

))}
) } export default Honors
